desc: Civic Carol Concert Get into the festive spirit at our annual carol concert in the beautiful surrounds of Walthamstow Assembly Hall. ?Join children and young people from Waltham Forest Music Service who will perform all your favourite carols interspersed with traditional readings from the Christmas story.? ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------- No booking required. ?Entry is free but donations are welcome on the door.
